_:Ncf73f401c0744b78bd3ad652b3f02b1f <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Paulette Simpson is the executive, corporate affairs and public policy at Jamaica National’s (JN) representative office in the United Kingdom (UK), and executive director of The Voice - Britain’s top black newspaper that has served the black community in the UK for 35 years.</p>\n" .
